â€œThought leadershipâ€ content is the harder of the two. Why? because it requires huge culture and skills changes in marketing departments. Media now trumps branded promotions, which threatens CMOs until they start hiring â€“ and thinking like â€“ journalists.
But my 2013 statement response to Skinner no longer holds up:
